text: This article is a list of events in the year 2003 in Mauritania. ==Incumbents== * President: Maaouya Ould Sid'Ahmed Taya * Prime Minister: **Cheikh El Avia Ould Mohamed Khouna **Sghair Ould M'Bareck ==Events== *September 19: The Maritime delimitation treaty between Mauritania and Cape Verde was signed ==Sports== *ASC Nasr de Sebkha won the Ligue 1 Mauritania football championship ==References== Category:2000s in Mauritania Category:Years of the 21st century in Mauritania Mauritania Mauritania
title: 2003 in Mauritania
